6.20	Peter_Vallone,_Jr.	Peter Vallone, Jr.	Peter F. Vallone Jr. is a member of the New York City Council representing the 22nd District, encompassing Astoria, Queens and the surrounding communities since 2002, succeeding his father, Peter Vallone, Sr.. He serves as Chair of the Council's Public Safety Committee, where he has led the fight against budget cuts affecting the New York City Police Department, put more officers in local precincts, and advocacy for state and federal funding for New York City.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/0c/Peter_F._Vallone_Jr..jpg/200px-Peter_F._Vallone_Jr..jpg
